    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "住寧波鄉之青蓮菴。",
        "translation": "He stayed at Qinglian'an in Ningpo Township.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c13_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "專修淨土。",
        "translation": "He was dedicated to cultivating the Pure Land.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c13_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "因病。",
        "translation": "He became ill.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c13_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "遂薙髮。",
        "translation": "He then had his hair cut.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c14_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "念淨土堂未曾完工。",
        "translation": "He was mindful that the Pure Land hall hadn't been completed yet.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c14_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "病中每抱憾。",
        "translation": "I always regretted it when I was ill.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c14_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有妙理法師者。",
        "translation": "There was this master, the Dharma Master Miaoli.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c14_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示之曰。",
        "translation": "He told him.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c15_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世事未了。",
        "translation": "\"The world's affairs have not yet been completed.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c15_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有人替汝。",
        "translation": "Someone will take over for you.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c15_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "生死事未了。",
        "translation": "The matters of birth and death have yet to be understood.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c15_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無人替汝。",
        "translation": "There's no one to take over for you.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c15_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今宜收下。",
        "translation": "Now, it's better to accept this.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c16_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一心歸命矣。",
        "translation": "With one mind, you can return to your life.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c16_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又有式教大師者。",
        "translation": "There's also the great teacher of the Siddha teaching.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c16_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "亦時來警策。",
        "translation": "He also comes from time to time to warn and counsel.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c16_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "遂默受善誡。",
        "translation": "He then quietly accepted the good admonition.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c17_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妄想芟除。",
        "translation": "He stifled false conceptions.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c17_19",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一日晨朝。",
        "translation": "One morning, he went to the morning office.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c17_20",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "忽謂大眾曰。",
        "translation": "Suddenly, he said to the crowd.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c17_21",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今日巳時可行。",
        "translation": "\"Today, it's feasible at 9:00 a.m.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c18_22",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或問曰。",
        "translation": "Some people asked.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c18_23",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "巳時向那里行。",
        "translation": "\"Where are you going at sunrise?",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c18_24",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "曰。",
        "translation": "They said.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c18_25",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝豈不知西行。",
        "translation": "\"Don't you know that you're going west?",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c18_26",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "至巳刻。",
        "translation": "By the time the sun was shining.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c19_27",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "果安然坐化。",
        "translation": "He really did sit down peacefully and pass away.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c19_28",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "論曰。",
        "translation": "The monk said.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c20_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善知識之恩。",
        "translation": "\"The kindness of a good teacher is greater than that of a father or mother.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c20_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大於父母。",
        "translation": "They're greater than parents.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c20_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "能使善根散而復聚。",
        "translation": "They can cause good roots to scatter and gather again.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c20_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀於明恒益信。",
        "translation": "Looking at them clearly and permanently, they'll increase their faith.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c20_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世之學人。",
        "translation": "People of learning in the world often don't know how to choose friends.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c21_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶往往不知擇友。",
        "translation": "They still often don't know how to choose a friend.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c21_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "悲夫。",
        "translation": "Pity.",
        "source": "X78n1552_002:0399c21_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
